          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "A Fun and Well-Organized Parents' Sports Event Chinmaya vidyalaya.\nI recently participated in the Parents' Sports Event at Chinmaya vidyalaya, held on 23 Nov 24, and it was an amazing experience. The event was well-organized, with a variety of sports and activities that allowed everyone to get involved. The staff were welcoming and created a positive and energetic environment for parents and students alike. The school's facilities were top-notch, making the day even more enjoyable. I especially appreciated how much effort was put into making this event not just about competition, but about having fun and fostering a sense of community. I highly recommend participating in future events at Chinmaya vidyalaya, and I’m excited for the next one!",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
