          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I chose Chinmaya School for my children because of its dedication to cultural values and heritage, and I’m extremely pleased with our experience. Since Subhashini Madam took charge, I've noticed a positive shift in the staff's approach, which is now more supportive and engaged. The school effectively balances academics with a variety of activities, providing a well-rounded experience for the students. Recently, I attended a 'Cook with Dad' session, which was a wonderful example of the school’s commitment to parental involvement and community building. I am hopeful that these positive changes continue, benefiting both our children and the school as a whole.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
